Feature: Data Scoping          Scenario: Users only see their own data     Given there are multiple users with data in the system     And I am logged in as a specific user     When I view my data       Then I should only see data belonging to me     And I should not see data belonging to other users    Scenario: User attempts to access another user's data     Given I am logged in     When I attempt to view another user's data     Then I should see an unauthorized access error message     And I should be redirected to my dashboard    Scenario: Ensure N+1 queries are optimized     Given there are 1000 users with associated data     When I view a page displaying data     Then the number of database queries should be optimized     And the page should load in a reasonable time